---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Uses — Hammadh Arquil"
  description="Hardware, software, and tools I use day-to-day."
>
  <article class="uses container-page">
    <header class="head">
      <p class="caption">/uses</p>
      <h1>Things I use</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Hardware, software, and tools I lean on day-to-day. Inspired by
        <a href="https://uses.tech" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">uses.tech</a>.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Hardware</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>MacBook Pro 14" (M4)</strong> — primary machine for code and design.</li>
        <li><strong>Gigabyte G24F</strong> — external display for the second window of code or Figma.</li>
        <li><strong>Armageddon MBA-61R</strong> — 60% mechanical, tactile switches.</li>
        <li><strong>Logitech MX Master 4</strong> — daily-driver mouse.</li>
        <li><strong>SteelSeries Arctis 5</strong> — wired headset, for actual focus.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Editor & terminal</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cursor</strong> — Tab autocomplete and agent mode; I drive the architecture, the agent does the typing. Small extension set (Prettier, ESLint, Astro, Tailwind IntelliSense).</li>
        <li><strong>Theme</strong> — default dark themes. I don't customise.</li>
        <li><strong>Font</strong> — JetBrains Mono in editor and terminal.</li>
        <li><strong>Terminal</strong> — zsh in Cursor's built-in terminal, default prompt.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Design</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Figma</strong> — UI design, prototyping, design tokens.</li>
        <li><strong>Adobe Photoshop & Illustrator</strong> — held over from my ElitePSD days; still useful for marks and stills.</li>
        <li><strong>After Effects</strong> — motion and micro-interactions.</li>
        <li><strong>CapCut</strong> — quick video edits and reels.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Stack of choice</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend</strong> — Next.js or Astro for SSR, React for interactive surfaces, Tailwind for styling, Flutter for mobile.</li>
        <li><strong>Backend</strong> — Node or Python depending on the workload, Postgres on Supabase, Cloudflare R2 for object storage.</li>
        <li><strong>Hosting</strong> — Vercel for apps; Cloudflare for DNS, CDN, and R2.</li>
        <li><strong>Auth</strong> — Supabase Auth.</li>
        <li><strong>AI</strong> — Azure AI Foundry, OpenAI APIs.</li>
        <li><strong>Billing</strong> — Polar.sh.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Productivity</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Notion</strong> — project notes, knowledge base.</li>
        <li><strong>Linear</strong> — issues, sprint planning.</li>
        <li><strong>GitHub</strong> — code, occasionally Issues.</li>
        <li><strong>Browser</strong> — Helium and Zen, depending on the context.</li>
        <li><strong>Music</strong> — Spotify or YouTube Music while coding.</li>
        <li><strong>Comms</strong> — Discord and WhatsApp.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <p class="footer-note">
      This page evolves slowly. Anything missing? <a href="mailto:hammadharquil@gmail.com">Tell me</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .uses {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .uses { padding-top: 3rem; }
  }
  .head { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .caption {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--fg-subtle);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .head h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: var(--leading-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .lede {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
  }
  .lede a, .footer-note a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  section {
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }
  section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  li {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
  }
  li strong {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .footer-note {
    color: var(--fg-subtle);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
</style>
